They are custom made inspired by 1678 2023 bearing blocks.

We have used them in the past two seasons and we have a very good experience with them.
In the first week of the season, we already knew we would use them so we started machining them very early.
They areâ€™t very complicated to manufacture but they do require two setups.
We machined the first setup and a good friend of ours helped us machine the second setup for better tolerance than what we could do.
